Output docs/demo-create.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/grove-demo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show
Type "./bin/grove"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "n"
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 300ms
Down
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Type "my-feature"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "q"
